summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5679 for the improvement of 49th Avenue Southwest, from West Graham Street to West Hudson Street; and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 75110, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
